<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: blazing spirit -->
  <BlazingSpirit.degreeDatas.blazing_spirit.label>炽热精神</BlazingSpirit.degreeDatas.blazing_spirit.label>
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] has an unbreakable spirit that inspires others. [PAWN_possessive] fiery determination makes [PAWN_objective] nearly immune to despair, though [PAWN_pronoun] needs constant activity. -->
  <BlazingSpirit.degreeDatas.blazing_spirit.description>[PAWN_nameDef]拥有鼓舞人心的不屈精神。[PAWN_pronoun]的强烈意志使旁人永不绝望，但这也让[PAWN_pronoun]需要持续活动。</BlazingSpirit.degreeDatas.blazing_spirit.description>
  
  <!-- EN: burning passion -->
  <BurningPassion.degreeDatas.burning_passion.label>热情如火</BurningPassion.degreeDatas.burning_passion.label>
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef]'s passionate nature drives [PAWN_objective] to excel at creative work, but [PAWN_pronoun] requires more recreation to maintain [PAWN_possessive] intense focus. -->
  <BurningPassion.degreeDatas.burning_passion.description>[PAWN_nameDef]天性热情，使[PAWN_pronoun]擅长艺术工作，但也需要更多娱乐保持高度专注力。</BurningPassion.degreeDatas.burning_passion.description>
  
  <!-- EN: combustive temper -->
  <CombustiveTemper.degreeDatas.combustive_temper.label>脾气易燃</CombustiveTemper.degreeDatas.combustive_temper.label>
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] has a volatile temperament that ignites into fury. When enraged, [PAWN_pronoun] becomes a devastating combatant but struggles with delicate work and has an unhealthy fascination with fire. -->
  <CombustiveTemper.degreeDatas.combustive_temper.description>[PAWN_nameDef]性情暴躁，容易愤怒。当[PAWN_pronoun]发怒时，就会化身狂战士。然而[PAWN_nameDef]不擅长精密作业，还对火焰有病态的迷恋。</CombustiveTemper.degreeDatas.combustive_temper.description>
  
  <!-- EN: forge master -->
  <ForgeMaster.degreeDatas.forge_master.label>锻造大师</ForgeMaster.degreeDatas.forge_master.label>
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] is a master of flame and forge. [PAWN_pronoun] works metal with unmatched skill and builds with the precision of a true craftsman. -->
  <ForgeMaster.degreeDatas.forge_master.description>[PAWN_nameDef]是火焰与锻造的大师。[PAWN_pronoun]的金属加工才能无与伦比，以真正工匠的专业眼光打造作品。</ForgeMaster.degreeDatas.forge_master.description>
  
  <!-- EN: inner fire -->
  <InnerFire.degreeDatas.inner_fire.label>内在之火</InnerFire.degreeDatas.inner_fire.label>
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] burns with an inner flame that protects [PAWN_objective] from cold but increases [PAWN_possessive] appetite. [PAWN_pronoun] excels at cooking and working with heat. -->
  <InnerFire.degreeDatas.inner_fire.description>[PAWN_nameDef]心中燃烧着火焰，使[PAWN_pronoun]不会受寒，但食欲也增加了。[PAWN_nameDef]很擅长料理和用火。</InnerFire.degreeDatas.inner_fire.description>
  
  <!-- EN: phoenix heart -->
  <PhoenixHeart.degreeDatas.phoenix_Heart.label>火鸟之心</PhoenixHeart.degreeDatas.phoenix_heart.label>
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] possesses remarkable regenerative abilities. Wounds heal faster and infections rarely take hold, as if [PAWN_possessive] body burns away impurities. -->
  <PhoenixHeart.degreeDatas.phoenix_heart.description>[PAWN_nameDef]再生能力惊人。[PAWN_pronoun]伤口愈合很快，鲜少发生感染，仿佛身躯能将杂质烧尽。</PhoenixHeart.degreeDatas.phoenix_heart.description>
  
</LanguageData>